#

Pumpkin Seed Yogurt Parfait

10 min
$3.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

DairyNuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

HealthyQuickBreakfast

Description

A creamy and crunchy parfait packed with the goodness of yogurt, pumpkin seeds, and fruits, perfect for a quick breakfast or snack!

Ingredients

  • greek yogurt: 1 cup
  • pumpkin seeds: 1/4 cup
  • honey or maple syrup: 1-2 tablespoons
  • fresh fruit (like berries or banana): 1/2 cup
  • granola (optional): 1/4 cup
